data.description: Gorgeous 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage home located in Westbury! You will find wood like tile throughout the entire home, no carpet! Gorgeous kitchen with granite countertops, designer style backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and white shaker soft close cabinetry perfect for making dinner. Vaulted and spacious living room! Spacious flex room upon entry the could be formal dining, living, office, gameroom or bedroom! Large primary bedroom with en-suite bathroom! Large backyard perfect for pets or gatherings!  AC system including ducts, furnace and hot water heater replaced in 2019. Stayed high and dry during Harvey! No HOA! Conveniently located just minutes away from shopping and dining! Medical center, sports stadiums, malls and within a short commute! Call and make your appointment today!
